# Performance

- Route bundle budget: 200 kB gzip warn, 350 kB gzip error.
- Route-level code splitting mandatory.
- Virtualize lists > 50 rows.
- Images: AVIF first, responsive `srcset`, lazy below the fold.
- LCP < 2.5s, INP < 200ms p75, CLS < 0.1.
- Memoize only with measured reason.
- Defer non-critical third-party scripts.
See `.opencode/agents/performance.md`.